#. Tag: title
#: details-institutions.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Institutions"
msgstr "Instituições"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Institutions in &kmymoney; serve as a way to group accounts. They are most "
"commonly financial institutions like banks and brokerage firms, but they can "
"be anything you want, such as <quote>Self</quote>, to hold accounts for the "
"cash in your pocket and any other assets not actually help by a financial "
"institution, or <quote>Stores</quote>, to group all your credit card and "
"other accounts with retail stores."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: details-institutions.docbook:22
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Institutions"
msgid "Institutions View"
msgstr "Instituições"

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:23
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Institutions view provides a summary of all the accounts grouped "
#| "under their respective institutions. The list of accounts under any "
#| "institution can be expanded or collapsed by clicking on the arrow to the "
#| "left of the institution name. The last listed institution is \"Accounts "
#| "with no institution assigned.\""
msgid ""
"The Institutions View provides a summary of all the accounts grouped under "
"their respective institutions. The list of accounts under any institution "
"can be expanded or collapsed by clicking on the arrow to the left of the "
"institution name. The last listed institution is \"Accounts with no "
"institution assigned.\""
msgstr ""
"O ecrã de Instituições oferece um resumo de todas as contas alojadas nas "
"suas respectivas instituições. Alista de contas em qualquer instituição pode "
"ser expandida ou fechada se carregar na seta à esquerda do nome da "
"instituição. A última instituição apresenta é \"Contas sem instituição "
"atribuída.\""

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:30
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Institutions view displays several columns, showing information about "
#| "the account. It also shows the total value of all accounts in each "
#| "institution. You can select which columns are shown by right clicking on "
#| "any column heading and selecting or unselecting the checkbox next to the "
#| "name of the column."
msgid ""
"The Institutions View displays several columns, showing information about "
"the account. It also shows the total value of all accounts in each "
"institution. You can select which columns are shown by right-clicking on any "
"column heading and selecting or unselecting the checkbox next to the name of "
"the column."
msgstr ""
"A área de Instituições mostra diversas colunas que apresentam informações "
"sobre a conta. Também mostra o valor total de todas as contas nessa "
"instituição. Poderá seleccionar as colunas que são apresentadas se carregar "
"com o botão direito em qualquer cabeçalho de coluna e marcar ou desmarcar a "
"opção ao lado do nome da coluna."

