msgid ""
"You must have a file open before you can create a new institution. If you do "
"not have an existing file, you will need to <link linkend=\"firsttime.newfile"
"\">create one</link>."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Deverá ter um ficheiro aberto antes de criar uma nova instituição. Se "
"não tiver um ficheiro existente, terá de <link linkend=\"firsttime.3\">criar "
"uma</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:163
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Only the name is required in the New Institution Dialog, all other fields "
#| "are optional. As with the personal information dialog, this data is not "
#| "currently used by &kmymoney;, but will be required by future releases for "
#| "certain features. In particular, the <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
#| "org/wiki/Bank_code\">Bank Code</ulink> and the <acronym> <ulink url="
#| "\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_9362\">BIC (Bank Identifier Code)</"
#| "ulink></acronym> will be required for online banking."
msgid ""
"Only the name is required in the New Institution Dialog, all other fields "
"are optional. As with the personal information dialog, this data is not "
"currently used by &kmymoney;, but some items may be required by future "
"releases for certain features. In particular, the <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_code\">Bank Code</ulink> and the <acronym> <ulink "
"url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_9362\">BIC (Bank Identifier Code)</"
"ulink></acronym> will be required for online banking, although this may "
"depend on the country your bank is in."
msgstr ""
"Só é obrigatório o nome na Janela de Nova Instituição, sendo todos os outros "
"campos opcionais. Como acontece na janela de informações pessoais, estes "
"dados não são usados de momento pelo &kmymoney;, mas serão necessários para "
"certas funcionalidades das versões futuras. Em particular, o <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_code\">Código do Banco</ulink> e o "
"<acronym><ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_9362\">BIC (Código "
"Identificador do Banco)</ulink></acronym> será obrigatórios na banca "
"'online'."

